1:07:49.319 --> 1:07:50.904
-Barry.
-No, no, listen.

1:07:51.655 --> 1:07:53.407
It's only right, okay?

1:07:53.490 --> 1:07:55.617
I came all the way here,

1:07:55.701 --> 1:07:57.870
and I was gonna put
a nice little sticky note on it.

1:08:00.497 --> 1:08:04.918
But here you are. So, I mean, I guess
the surprise factor is kind of kaput.

1:08:05.002 --> 1:08:08.714
