I'm done with surprises for tonight.

1:08:08.797 --> 1:08:10.883
-Aren't we all?
-Babe, I messed up.

1:08:10.966 --> 1:08:13.135
I came to work today,
I'll catch up on some sales,

1:08:13.218 --> 1:08:15.888
and then I guess
I got caught up, I messed up.

1:08:15.971 --> 1:08:16.971
As usual.

1:08:19.015 --> 1:08:20.475
Baby, you should go.

1:08:20.559 --> 1:08:24.270
You know, this ain't for me anymore,
I'm an asshole, so...

1:08:24.354 --> 1:08:25.606
No, you're not an asshole.

1:08:25.689 --> 1:08:28.317
