1:08:32.821 --> 1:08:35.157
That's what I love about you,
you always call.

1:08:48.002 --> 1:08:52.466
Okay, we're gonna go. Yeah.

1:08:54.051 --> 1:08:56.178
-No. Barry, let's go.
-Wait, no.

1:08:56.261 --> 1:08:57.845
I want to leave this for the guru.

1:08:57.930 --> 1:09:00.015
Barry, we need to go. Barry!

1:09:00.098 --> 1:09:03.018
Hey. Hey, don't you
fucking touch her, man!

1:09:03.560 --> 1:09:05.062
-Oh, my God!
-Hey!

1:09:07.064 --> 1:09:10.234
Asa. Hey, hey.
This is going way too far, man.

1:09:10.317 --> 1:09:14.279
