1:23:32.221 --> 1:23:33.889
I can't help but feel silly.

1:23:36.016 --> 1:23:37.017
But you'll feel better.

1:23:39.269 --> 1:23:41.605
And besides, silly is your middle name.

1:23:41.688 --> 1:23:43.106
Silly is my middle name.

1:23:45.234 --> 1:23:46.151
So wise.

1:23:48.695 --> 1:23:49.696
-Okay.
-Yeah.

1:24:13.345 --> 1:24:14.179
Mrs. Hanks!

1:24:15.180 --> 1:24:16.557
Bring your ass outside!
